      "span_text": "Pretreatment of the mycelial powder Prior to the extraction of the polysaccharides, a supercritical fluid carbon dioxide (SC-CO 2 , 99.5% in purity) extraction was performed to remove some inherently existing oil soluble substances in order to minimize the interference to the polysaccharides, according to a previous report [CITATION_1] .",
